  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slime Nomi is a pixelated platformer. Help Nomi collect potion ingredients with the help of unique mechanics in various hand-crafted levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/68dc949e769707d467bd3e1731093f30.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" width=960 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/68dc949e769707d467bd3e1731093f30.webm?t=1770343974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/68dc949e769707d467bd3e1731093f30.mp4?t=1770343974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/a74fb0a5f91361fd6b237ab832c9d441.webp?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/a74fb0a5f91361fd6b237ab832c9d441.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=16 /></picture></span>A variety of unique mechanics<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/a74fb0a5f91361fd6b237ab832c9d441.webp?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/a74fb0a5f91361fd6b237ab832c9d441.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=16 /></picture></span>: Over ten original mechanics! Each chapter brings a whole new experience to the player. Teleport potions, jam jars, wisps that can pass through walls, shields, explosive bricks... the game is loaded with creative ideas. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/47b46c3aab6a01568ab2ccd80cd019c3.apng?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/47b46c3aab6a01568ab2ccd80cd019c3.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=19 height=19 /></picture></span>Varied level design<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/47b46c3aab6a01568ab2ccd80cd019c3.apng?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/47b46c3aab6a01568ab2ccd80cd019c3.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=19 height=19 /></picture></span>: Hundreds of well-designed levels blending different mechanics. Each level has a different route and experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/ec8f31b79c876d22907f6c99281eff8f.apng?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/ec8f31b79c876d22907f6c99281eff8f.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=18 /></picture></span>Cute pixel art<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/ec8f31b79c876d22907f6c99281eff8f.apng?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/ec8f31b79c876d22907f6c99281eff8f.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=18 /></picture></span>: Smooth pixel art animations and widely different scenes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/3cb64c54d813d353f6ac310ec529f2b9.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" width=21 height=21 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/3cb64c54d813d353f6ac310ec529f2b9.webm?t=1770343974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Story mode with moderate difficulty<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/3cb64c54d813d353f6ac310ec529f2b9.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" width=21 height=21 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/3cb64c54d813d353f6ac310ec529f2b9.webm?t=1770343974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>: Difficulty of story mode increases gradually and slowly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/f0f7586e3a158668f58d9c5a9801464e.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" width=16 height=16 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/f0f7586e3a158668f58d9c5a9801464e.webm?t=1770343974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Map and collectible marks<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/f0f7586e3a158668f58d9c5a9801464e.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" width=16 height=16 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/f0f7586e3a158668f58d9c5a9801464e.webm?t=1770343974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>: Level map can be unlocked early in story mode. The map has marks of savepoints and collectibles, making it easier to explore and collect things.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/3064956336e815a74eb85c35a218bd1e.apng?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/3064956336e815a74eb85c35a218bd1e.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=12 height=20 /></picture></span>Custom options<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/3064956336e815a74eb85c35a218bd1e.apng?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/3064956336e815a74eb85c35a218bd1e.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=12 height=20 /></picture></span>: Provide help to beat challenging levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/6078c30ec2a9d92da7dc70c0630fea67.apng?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/6078c30ec2a9d92da7dc70c0630fea67.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=16 height=23 /></picture></span>Extra levels<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/6078c30ec2a9d92da7dc70c0630fea67.apng?t=1770343974\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/6078c30ec2a9d92da7dc70c0630fea67.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" class=\"bb_img\" width=16 height=23 /></picture></span>: Extra levels have Innovative ideas that are not in the main game. Piano music mix platforming, match-three mix platforming, innovative mahjong game... brilliant ideas everywhere!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/35f7708b8ce555b02e593638bc809859.poster.avif?t=1770343974\" width=960 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/35f7708b8ce555b02e593638bc809859.webm?t=1770343974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934150/extras/35f7708b8ce555b02e593638bc809859.mp4?t=1770343974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
